company_overview: The company is engaged in private hospitals with the main focus on optimal health services. At present, the company manages type C hospitals located in various strategic areas, namely Kedungwaringin, Sukatani, and Cibadak. As a type C hospital, in accordance with the Minister of Health Regulation Article 16 paragraph (1) concerning Classification and Licensing of Hospitals issued by the Ministry of Health of the Republic of Indonesia, this hospital is required to have a minimum capacity of 100 beds to meet comprehensive health service standards.
